# Implementation Logic

Read the **Implementation Logic** section of `docs/ai/cap-coding-standards.md`.

For AI/LLM code, also read `docs/ai/sap-ai-sdk-guide.md`.

## Rules

- Export a single `async function(req)` (or `async function(results, req)` for after handlers)
- Use CQL: `const { SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE } = cds.ql;`
- Use `cds.connect.to()` for external services
- Use `req.reject()` / `req.error()` for error handling
- Use `@sap-ai-sdk/foundation-models` for LLM calls, never generic OpenAI SDK
